{"id":"e8c1cd3a-a18f-4b68-b954-f4dd90ebc349","title":"八正道","slug":"art-e8c1cd3a","category":"佛學","categorySlug":"buddhism","tags":["八正道","佛學"],"updatedAt":"2026-02-03","excerpt":"八正道是佛教指導教徒修行、通往解脫（涅槃）的八種正確途徑，屬於四聖諦中的「道諦」，即：正見、正思惟、正語、正業、正命、正精進、正念、正定。這八項原則涵蓋了智慧、倫理與禪定，旨在修正身、口、意三業，是遠離苦海、趨向自在的具體實踐法門。 八正道","readingMin":1,"isNew":false,"html":"<p>八正道是佛教指導教徒修行、通往解脫（涅槃）的八種正確途徑，屬於四聖諦中的「道諦」，即：<strong>正見、正思惟、正語、正業、正命、正精進、正念、正定</strong>。這八項原則涵蓋了智慧、倫理與禪定，旨在修正身、口、意三業，是遠離苦海、趨向自在的具體實踐法門。</p>\n<p>八正道通常被歸納為「三無漏學」（戒、定、慧）：</p>\n<p><strong>一、 智慧（慧）</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%8B&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgAEAg&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正見</a></strong><strong> (Right View)</strong>：正確的見解。如理理解四聖諦、因果法則、緣起性空，捨棄邪見。</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%9D%E6%83%9F&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgAEAo&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正思惟</a></strong><strong> (Right Intention)</strong>：正確的思考。遠離貪、瞋、癡，以慈悲心和出離心進行理性思考。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>二、 倫理行為（戒）</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E8%AA%9E&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgAEA4&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正語</a></strong><strong> (Right Speech)</strong>：正確的言語。不妄語（說謊）、不兩舌（挑撥）、不惡口（罵人）、不綺語（輕浮話），說話清淨。</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E6%A5%AD&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgAEBA&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正業</a></strong><strong> (Right Action)</strong>：正確的行為。不殺生、不偷盜、不邪淫，行為清淨。</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E5%91%BD&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgAEBI&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正命</a></strong><strong> (Right Livelihood)</strong>：正確的謀生。以正當、不損害他人的職業來維持生計。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>三、 精神鍛鍊（定）</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E7%B2%BE%E9%80%B2&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgBEAE&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正精進</a></strong><strong> (Right Effort)</strong>：正確的努力。勤修正法，止惡揚善，斷除邪念，培養善念。</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E5%BF%B5&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgCEAE&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正念</a></strong><strong> (Right Mindfulness)</strong>：正確的意念。專注於當下，時時覺知身、受、心、法（四念處），保持清醒覺照。</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=%E6%AD%A3%E5%AE%9A&amp;sca_esv=1cf3b1e2cbd119f3&amp;biw=1024&amp;bih=473&amp;aic=0&amp;sxsrf=ANbL-n5Tb9fDxfYWv70Wlz6dioa5DateWQ%3A1770077945486&amp;ei=-T6Bac6wHanT1e8P0fan4Q8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiB-OG6hrySAxUzkq8BHVDdKEsQgK4QegYIAQgDEAE&amp;uact=5&amp;oq=%E5%85%AB%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93&amp;gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiCeWFq-ato-&amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">正定</a></strong><strong> (Right Concentration)</strong>：正確的禪定。身心安定，遠離雜念，進入專注的禪定狀態，智慧由此而生。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>八正道並非八個獨立的步驟，而是互為因果、環環相扣，共同構成「中道」的修行生活。</p>\n","headings":[],"prev":{"slug":"art-8c6f04c4","title":"十二因緣"},"next":{"slug":"art-2e0a49d2","title":"四聖諦的具體內涵"}}